                  </hi>. I saw Samuel Elliott holding the prisoner—I missed two pairs of shoes—he said he was going to buy them, but had only got 2<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.—they are worth 6<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 6<hi rend="italic">d</hi>.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I never ran away, and never gave any shoes away; I intended to leave a deposit for them.</p>
